Eurorack DSP (Émilie Gillet)
----------------------------

NOODLERACK includes WebAssembly builds of DSP code from Émilie Gillet's
eurorack repository:

- Plaits, used by RAMEN
- Marbles, used by BOBA
- Rings, used by UDON
- Tides 2018, used by SLURP
- Clouds, used by STEAM

The upstream DSP code is copyright Emilie Gillet and is licensed under the MIT
License. The MIT license text for this code is included in LICENSE.

Upstream source: https://github.com/pichenettes/eurorack

